# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Center-Impact:
#   Strengthened/Weakened/Created/Dissolved: [center] - [why]
#
# Contact:
#   Success-if: [what confirms this worked]
#   Failure-if: [what would show this failed]
#
# --- For non-trivial changes, add: ---
# Aim: [problem being solved]
# Claim: [what this enables]
# Assumptions: [load-bearing beliefs]
# Evidence: [what motivated this]
#
# --- Common types: ---
# strengthen, create, dissolve, revision, simplify, refactor, chore
#
# --- Critical: ---
# If you can't specify what would make this WRONG, it's mythology.
